  "Description": {
    "English": "Non-violent projectile weapon. Launched projectiles will incapacitate nearby targets with a burst of electrical energy. Effective against both biological and electronic entities.<br> <br>Charged with <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Unstable Plasma</span>.<br> <br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> to activate.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "非致命性投射武器。此武器发射的投射物可释放电能冲击瘫痪周遭目标，能够有效对抗生命体与电子设备。<br><br>充能需要消耗<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定的等离子</span>。<br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>激活武器。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "「非暴力」射彈武器。發射的射彈會發出一道電能癱瘓附近的目標。對生物和電子存在體都有效。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不穩定電漿</span>充能。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 啟動。"
  },
